# 🕒 Digital Clock

A simple digital clock built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. This project displays the current time in a 24-hour format and updates every second.

## 🔧 Technologies Used

- **HTML** – Markup structure
- **CSS** – Styling for layout and appearance
- **JavaScript** – Logic to update time dynamically

## 🚀 Features

- Displays real-time hours, minutes, and seconds
- Responsive design (works on desktop and mobile)
- Clean and minimalist user interface

